<h3>Warning</h3>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
<p><span class="label label-warning">Warning</span>
<p>Your account will be blocked in case there is more than 10 times incorrect password input.</p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
<a class="btn btn-warning" href="#">OK</a>
</div>
</div>

