         </tbody>
      </table>
       <h5>How to Use</h5>
<p><b>What is Information Message?</b></p>
	<p>An information message is to alert users useful and relevant, but never critical information. It like a notification to let user know a specific information.<br>E.g: Your account has been registered successfully. Please go to your email address box to activate your account.</p>
	<p><b>Characteristic of a good information message</b></p>
	<li>Useful. The information let user know something new or has been done successfully.</li>
	<li>Asynchronous. The information is not an immediate, action required in information message can be postponed.</li>
	<li>Relevant. The information is helpful that user may already know.</li><br>
	<p><b>What should be avoided in an information message?</b></p>
	<li>Redundant. The message includes many redundant information<br> E.g: In Answers, submit a question successfully, there is a information pop up display that does not close automatically. So, users have to click OK to close the pop-up that is inconvenient. </li>
	<li>Annoying. The message displays too much that is not necessary.<br> E.g: These selected files have been deleted successfully.</li>
	<li>Actionable. The information does not require immediate action</li>
<h3><a name="S4"></a><span>Confirmation Message</span></h3>
          <h5>Template</h5>
         <div class="modal" style="position: relative; top: auto; left: auto; margin: 0 auto 20px; z-index: 1; max-width: 100%;">
<div class="modal-header">
<button class="close" aria-hidden="true" data-dismiss="modal" type="button">×</button>
<h3>Confirmation</h3>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
<p><span class="label">Confirm</span>
<p>Are you sure you want to delete this driver and all its data?</p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
<button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
<button class="btn btn-primary">OK</button>
</div>
</div>

<div id="myModal3" class="modal hide fade" aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" role="dialog" tabindex="-1" style="display: block;">
<div class="modal-header">
<button class="close" aria-hidden="true" data-dismiss="modal" type="button">x</button>
<h3>Confirmation</h3>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
<p><span class="label">Confirm</span>
<p>Are you sure you want to delete this driver and all its data?</p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
<button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
<button class="btn btn-primary">OK</button>
</div>
</div>

